{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 A convenient way to snap envelope point values to semitones for Pitch Wheel automation. Plus/minus 12 semitones.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Currently 2 versions for Main tcpfx envelope lane and tcpfx Automation items (AI).\par}
