{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li360 \fi-360 4)\tx360\tab When the "Run" script is executed with its shortcut, it will run the armed Mouse editing script.\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 By using this feature, each "Mouse editing" script does need not be linked to its own shortcut key. Instead, only the accompanying "Run" script needs to be linked to a shortcut.\par}
