{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs36 ReaLauncher\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 A custom version of the startup prompt window for loading (recent) projects, project/track templates and more with additional features.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Uses 'Lokasenna's GUI library v2 for Lua' as base: https://forum.cockos.com/showthread.php?t=177772. Big thanks to Lokasenna for his work!!\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs32 Main features\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Separate tabs for [Recent Projects], (.rpp) [Project Templates], (.rtracktemplate) [Track Templates], (.rpp) Projects, (.rpl) [Project Lists], (.rpp-bak) [Backups] and (.pdf) [Docs]\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Option to set additional folder paths for [Project Templates] and [Track Templates] (which are used in addition to the default template folders)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Option to set custom folder paths for [Projects], [Project Lists], [Backups] and [Docs] tabs\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab List filter in each tab that supports the use of multiple search words separated by a 'space' character\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Global section with [New Tab], [New Project] and [Open Project] buttons\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Selection and loading of multiple entries at once (multi-select via mouse is already part of Lokasenna's GUI library)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab File paths can be shown/hidden\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab 'Keep open' checkbox to switch the automatic closing behavior of the window\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Scalable and resizeable window\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs32 Features that require SWS Extensions (2.9.8 or higher):\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab [Docs] tab for listing .pdf files\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab [Recent Projects] tab for listing and managing the recent projects (with functions to remove selected entries and clearing the entire list)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab [Show in Explorer/Finder] button to search for the location of a selected file\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Setup of predefined Reaper Theme Slots and the possibility to switch between them (uses SWS Resources)\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs32 Features that require js_ReaScriptAPI (0.991 or higher):\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Function to preview attached 'demo' audio files (supported file extensions: .wav, .flac, .mp3 and .ogg)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Option for adding folder paths in the [Options] tab via a 'Browse' dialog (besides manual copy & paste)\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs32 Discussion thread\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 https://forum.cockos.com/showthread.php?t=208697\par}
}

