{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs36 Adjusts the colors of any ReaperTheme/ReaperThemeZip\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Theme supports both zipped and unzipped themes\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Offers Brightness, Contrast and Gamma adjustments\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Tooltips to always inform user of what is happening\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab A/B Button to toggle between the current setting and the original theme colors\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Use the Take Snapshot button to store settings and make new adjustments on these rather than the original theme's colors\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Take Snapshot button: left-click to add new, right-click to replace current selected\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab The Snapshots are the base colors on which you make adjustments using the sliders\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab The adjustments are applied to the selected color groups in the Color Groups Tab. The rest of the theme colors are copied over\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab In the Color Groups Tab you can inspect or change the theme colors on which the adjustments apply\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab In the Listbox you can choose (click) or delete (Alt-click) your saved Snapshots\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab If you change the Color Groups selection, and the new selection includes groups of the previous selection, a Snapshot is automatically taken\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab UNDO/REDO buttons to undo/redo adjustments made on the selected theme color Snapshot in the Listbox\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab User is prompted to save when exiting and if there were color changes in comparison to the original theme\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab If user changes theme while the script is running, script automatically closes and prompts user to save if there were any changes\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab The new saved adjusted theme inherits the old theme's "Default_6.0 theme adjuster" settings, if any\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Script Requires Lokasenna GUI v2 and JS_ReaScriptAPI to work. Both are checked if they exist at the start of the script\sa180\par}
