{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs36 If there is a selected item inside the time selection then mode = sel item auto punch\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs36 If no time selection but selected item after play or edit cursor then mode = sel item auto punch\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs36 If no time sel and no sel item after play or edit cursor then mode = normal\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs36 If already recording then running the script stops recording\par}
